From a1ac15c81d194a19a586f591f82763a2d3a6d286 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 18:19:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Security hardening, UX enhancements, and repo cleanup
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Security:
- Add DOMPurify CDN for XSS prevention on user-generated HTML
- Apply esc() sanitization to all user-controlled innerHTML (names, bios,
  post bodies, announcement content, fame captions, content metadata)
- Add login rate limiting: 5 failed attempts triggers 15-min lockout,
  tracked per email in localStorage
- Add session persistence: currentUser restored from localStorage on page
  refresh (password never stored, only id/role/tier)
- Block deactivated and pending accounts from signing in with clear messages
- Admin login now also rate-limited

Member approval workflow:
- New enrollments land in 'pending' status instead of instant 'active'
- Admin members panel shows Approve button for pending members
- Enrollment success message updated to explain pending review
- Login blocked for pending accounts with helpful messaging

Admin panel — member table improvements:
- Live search by name, email, or tier
- Filter dropdowns for tier and status
- Pagination (25 per page) with pending members always shown first
- Pending members highlighted and Approve button visible
- New Status column added alongside Role

Learning Exchange — content search:
- Search input added above filter tabs
- Filters by title, description, author, or programme window in real-time
- Empty state message adapts to show search term

UX improvements:
- Email subscribe popup now uses sessionStorage — shows once per browser
  session instead of being permanently dismissible
- Confirmation dialogs added for: Remove from Wall of Fame, Delete
  announcement, Delete financial report (were missing, now consistent
  with the existing pattern on content and post deletions)
- Slide images: only first 3 preloaded immediately; rest deferred to
  requestIdleCallback / 3s timeout — faster initial page load

Repo cleanup:
- Add .gitignore (backup files, OS files, editor dirs, env files, logs)
- Remove 19 backup/copy files committed to the repo root

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
